"(define (send-for-global-and-detailed-place circuit)
  "Return global placement result."
  (send-for-placement (Composite->place-spec
                      circuit
                      #:place-nsteps 50
                      #:place-nbins 300
                        ;; do not do detailed placement
                      #:sa-ncycles 10
                      #:sa-nsteps 3000
                      #:sa-stepsize 10
                      ;; to support rotation, use non-0 e.g. 0.3
                      #:sa-theta-stepsize 0)))"
